Title: More Fun with High-Voltage Toys
Book Description: 'This lively interactive session is for those interested in obtaining- building- fondling- and occasionally (accidentally?) hurting themselves with clocks- spinners- glowers- thermometers- blinking lights- nixies- VFDs- dekatrons. Demonstrations of how to make a clock in 10 minutes for less than $100 in parts and newbie skills.  '
